Third-party content
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project deploys an audit ruleset that is the work of a third party and is
redistributed UNMODIFIED under its own license:

    Linux Audit Daemon - Best Practice Configuration
    Copyright Florian Roth / Nextron Systems
    https://github.com/Neo23x0/auditd
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

At runtime the installer downloads the latest version of this ruleset from the
upstream repository. If the download is unavailable, it falls back to a
self-contained copy embedded in install-auditd-rules.sh (see the
print_embedded_rules function), which preserves the original header and
attribution. All credit for the audit ruleset belongs to its original author.
